    <item>
      <title>最高法院被要求阻止德克萨斯州移民驱逐法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-asked-to-block-law-letting-texas-deport-migrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府要求美国最高法院阻止德克萨斯州一项允许该州逮捕并驱逐非法入境者的法律，这为法院的选举年日历增添了又一​​个带有政治色彩的案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-asked-to-block-law-letting-texas-deport-migrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:12:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国发现哈马斯自 10 月 7 日以来实施性暴力的证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/un-cites-evidence-hamas-committed-sexual-violence-since-oct-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国找到了“合理的理由”得出结论，哈马斯在 10 月 7 日袭击以色列期间实施了性暴力，并表示有迹象表明此类暴力行为仍在继续针对被该组织扣为人质的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/un-cites-evidence-hamas-committed-sexual-violence-since-oct-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国资助协议对司法部对苹果、Ticketmaster 的反垄断调查造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-funding-deal-delivers-blow-to-doj-antitrust-probes-of-apple-ticketmaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项让联邦政府在 9 月份保持运转的支出协议将限制反垄断执法机构可获得的资金，这可能会阻碍对苹果公司和 Live Nation Entertainment Inc. 旗下 Ticketmaster 的高调调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-funding-deal-delivers-blow-to-doj-antitrust-probes-of-apple-ticketmaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:31:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦总理下令与国际货币基金组织开始贷款谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/pakistan-pm-sharif-orders-starting-talks-with-imf-for-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦总理谢巴兹·谢里夫指示当局加快与国际货币基金组织的谈判，该国 30 亿美元的救助计划将于 4 月结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/pakistan-pm-sharif-orders-starting-talks-with-imf-for-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:30:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海地暴力越狱引发谋杀和骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/prison-break-after-violent-gang-raid-sparks-emergency-in-haiti</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，全副武装的团伙袭击了该国两座最大的监狱，暴力事件席卷了首都，海地宣布进入紧急状态，并实施夜间宵禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/prison-break-after-violent-gang-raid-sparks-emergency-in-haiti</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
